# Enforce LF line endings across all text files so adapter emit and bundle
# tests stay platform-stable. Without this, Windows checkouts (with
# core.autocrlf=true) produce CRLF working trees while Linux CI runners
# produce LF, and any test that hashes emitted files would diverge per-
# platform.
#
# `* text=auto eol=lf` lets git auto-detect text vs binary; binaries are
# left untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
